title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Oct 20 2021

description:
Shocking new data reveals Biden's border crisis is deteriorating further with 1.7 million illegal immigrants invading the US in 2021. "It's the Border, Stupid!" should be a 2022 campaign slogan. Clay says it's a guaranteed winner. How prepared are Clay and Buck for Halloween? Clay has a giant dragon decoration at his house. Man accused of raping woman on crowded train was released from immigration detention, never deported. Train passengers recorded the incident on phones, didn't call 911 as woman was raped on Philadelphia train.
